        <img class="thumbnail" src="https://static.standard.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2017/05/24/16/shutterstock-138370757.jpg?width=850&&fit=bounds&format=pjpg&auto=webp&quality=70">
        <p>A petite seaside town most notable for its harbour (worth Instagramming) and its oysters — the annual festival started this week. The small streets are teeming with day trippers hunting through charity shops, and the beach is overflowing with boaties and windsurfers.</p>
        <div class="callout">
