        <img class="thumbnail" src="https://static.standard.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2017/05/24/16/shutterstock-514688542.jpg?width=850&fit=bounds&format=pjpg&auto=webp&quality=70">
        <p>A quintessentially English fishing village with traditional cockle sheds, working boats and a tiny sandy beach is London’s closest coastal patch, in neighbouring Essex.</p>
        <div class="callout">
